# RE7 21 — Project Conventions

## Stack

React 19.2.4 · Vite 6 · GSAP 3.12 · Tailwind CSS 3.4 · JavaScript ESM (no TypeScript)

## Do not

- Run `npm run dev` — the dev server is always running in watch mode
- Create `.env` files — none are needed
- Add external state libraries (Redux, Zustand, etc.) — state lives in `useReducer` in `GameTable.jsx`
- Add a router library — screen routing is a single `useState` in `App.jsx`
- Import from `src/engine/` inside components except for constants/enums used for display

## File structure

```
src/engine/        ← pure game logic, no React
src/components/    ← React UI, reads state and dispatches actions
src/assets/trumps/ ← PNG trump card images from RE Fandom Wiki
```

## CLAUDE.md

`CLAUDE.md` in the project root contains full AI context including state shape, ROUND_STATE flow diagram, and documented gotchas. Read it before making significant changes to game logic.

## Commit policy

Never commit unless the user explicitly asks. Never push. Never amend past commits.
